$ Python standard library: textwrap
@ textwrap

{ fill

  Format text to fit into a specific output-width, measured in characters.

  gh|about-python|/standard-library/textwrap/fill.py||

 `textwrap.wrap()` returns the «filled» text in a → development/languages/Python/types/list of strings.

}
{ dedent

  Remove leading whitespace from *triple-quoted* strings:

  gh|about-python|/standard-library/textwrap/dedent.py||

}

